title: Macbook 820-00165 No Boot
message:
SMC and U6100 is already reballed or replaced. Flux all around.

C0892 was corodded. Replaced.

Getting all voltages at U1950

What can be the issue?

title: Macbook 820-00165 No Boot
message:
Did the machine arrived with BIOS chip reworked?
If yes, flash known good BIOS, clean ME.
